---
title: Seared Lamb Rump & Bengal Coconut Sauce with Spiced Veggies & Cucumber Raita
description: It's roast lamb, but not as you know it! We're using our mild, yet flavourful Bengal curry paste to lift succulent lamb rump to new heights. A classy side of roasted spiced potatoes and cauliflower with flaked almonds is all that's needed to create a meal fit for a maharajah!
